# CircuitPython Library Dependencies for MTA LED Sign
# Copy these libraries to your CIRCUITPY/lib/ folder

## Required Library Folders:
adafruit_bitmap_font/
adafruit_bus_device/
adafruit_display_shapes/
adafruit_display_text/
adafruit_esp32spi/
adafruit_imageload/
adafruit_io/
adafruit_matrixportal/
adafruit_minimqtt/
adafruit_portalbase/

## Required .mpy Files:
adafruit_connection_manager.mpy
adafruit_fakerequests.mpy
adafruit_requests.mpy
adafruit_ticks.mpy
neopixel.mpy
neopixel_spi.mpy
simpleio.mpy

## Download Source:
Get these from the CircuitPython Community Bundle:
https://circuitpython.org/libraries

## Notes:
- tom-thumb.bdf font file goes in /fonts/ folder (not /lib/)
- secrets.py goes in root directory (not /lib/)
- Total size: ~2-3MB of libraries
